originalText.text: Dale has been an absolute pleasure to work with. My wife and I trust her implicitly for the quality of work and design sense. With Dale, we know we're getting top shelf design and service delivered by a friendly, high-touch professional. She gets us and designs with our tastes foremost in mind.

originalText.text: I saw some of Dale’s work at Gracie Mansion — she and her team helped re-do the house during its last major facelift.  I also saw some of Dale’s contributions to the new Drama Book Store.  Both important projects had a high level of quality and a wonderful sense of permanent relevance — solid, substantial and timeless.

originalText.text:
We used Dale Cohen Design studio two times over the last several years to design and update our apartment and renovate our kitchen. Her designs were perfect: creative and inventive. She understood our particular needs and tastes and was sensitive to our budgetary concerns. She made herself very available for consultations, provided extremely timely feedback and was accessible in every way.
Highly recommend
